00:13:54,334 --> 00:13:55,381
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What's going on?</i></b></font>

327
00:13:55,460 --> 00:13:57,053
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, I thought you weren't
getting home till 8:00.</i></b></font>

328
00:13:57,128 --> 00:13:59,256
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's 8:30. I guess I
lost track of time.</i></b></font>

329
00:13:59,339 --> 00:14:01,512
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I have just been buried
in this paperwork.</i></b></font>

330
00:14:01,591 --> 00:14:04,515
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, I can see that.
Are we being audited?</i></b></font>

331
00:14:05,845 --> 00:14:06,971
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Igor a job.</i></b></font>

332
00:14:07,263 --> 00:14:08,560
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I would have
called you right away</i></b></font>

333
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:10,892
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I've been swamped from the
minute I walked into the clinic.</i></b></font>

334
00:14:10,975 --> 00:14:13,023
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You got a job
at a legal clinic?</i></b></font>

335
00:14:13,102 --> 00:14:14,382
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mike, that's amazing.</i></b></font>

336
00:14:14,395 --> 00:14:15,567
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, it is.</i></b></font>

337
00:14:16,272 --> 00:14:18,320
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Um... And yes, they
know about me.</i></b></font>

338
00:14:18,524 --> 00:14:20,822
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>In fact, it's the
reason I got hired.</i></b></font>

339
00:14:20,902 --> 00:14:22,028
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Let me guess.</i></b></font>

340
00:14:22,111 --> 00:14:23,511
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They were smart enough
to appreciate</i></b></font>

341
00:14:23,529 --> 00:14:25,031
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>they can get someone
with your experience</i></b></font>

342
00:14:25,114 --> 00:14:26,866
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>for 10 cents
on the dollar.</i></b></font>

343
00:14:26,949 --> 00:14:28,121
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You got it.</i></b></font>

344
00:14:28,242 --> 00:14:32,122
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>$35,000 a year,
to be exact.</i></b></font>

345
00:14:32,205 --> 00:14:33,252
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mmm.</i></b></font>

346
00:14:33,331 --> 00:14:37,211
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which means that we should probably
start packing up the place now,</i></b></font>

347
00:14:37,293 --> 00:14:40,263
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>because we definitely cannot
afford to live here anymore.</i></b></font>

348
00:14:40,838 --> 00:14:44,388
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I would live
in a shoebox with you</i></b></font>

349
00:14:44,467 --> 00:14:45,844
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>if it meant
you were happy.</i></b></font>

350
00:14:45,927 --> 00:14:48,100
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh. I think you meant that
you would live in a shoebox</i></b></font>

351
00:14:48,179 --> 00:14:50,728
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>as long as the Thai
place still delivered.</i></b></font>

352
00:14:51,140 --> 00:14:52,392
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And the sushi place.</i></b></font>

353
00:14:52,475 --> 00:14:53,567
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Of course.</i></b></font>

354
00:14:57,939 --> 00:14:59,156
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You want one?</i></b></font>

355
00:14:59,357 --> 00:15:00,483
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You kidding me?</i></b></font>

356
00:15:00,608 --> 00:15:02,736
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>After reading Pinkalicious
for the seventh time?</i></b></font>

357
00:15:02,819 --> 00:15:04,366
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I need a six-pack.</i></b></font>

358
00:15:11,244 --> 00:15:13,087
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It was nice
putting them to bed.</i></b></font>

359
00:15:13,788 --> 00:15:14,789
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, yeah.</i></b></font>

360
00:15:14,872 --> 00:15:18,251
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Let's hear you say that after
doing it 365 days a year.</i></b></font>

361
00:15:18,334 --> 00:15:20,462
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I thought Katie put them
to bed most nights.</i></b></font>

362
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:21,762
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah.</i></b></font>

363
00:15:21,838 --> 00:15:23,260
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was saying it for her.</i></b></font>

364
00:15:25,049 --> 00:15:27,177
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thanks for making me
stay over, Marcus.</i></b></font>

365
00:15:30,513 --> 00:15:32,607
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, maybe after
tomorrow night,</i></b></font>

366
00:15:33,015 --> 00:15:34,562
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you could do it more often.</i></b></font>

367
00:15:37,562 --> 00:15:38,779
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe.</i></b></font>

368
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:44,618
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thank you all
for coming.</i></b></font>

369
00:15:45,903 --> 00:15:47,120
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm Lily.</i></b></font>

370
00:15:47,738 --> 00:15:50,332
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was married to Gordon
for almost 30 years.</i></b></font>

371
00:15:51,075 --> 00:15:53,043
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We didn't make it
the whole 30,</i></b></font>

372
00:15:53,494 --> 00:15:56,839
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and for a long time, I considered
myself a failure because of that.</i></b></font>

373
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,337
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But Gordon didn't.</i></b></font>

374
00:16:01,002 --> 00:16:02,754
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>A few years
after our divorce,</i></b></font>

375
00:16:02,837 --> 00:16:06,011
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I wanted to apologize
for things not working out.</i></b></font>

376
00:16:08,426 --> 00:16:10,053
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He just smiled and said,</i></b></font>

377
00:16:11,387 --> 00:16:14,061
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"Lily, what the hell
are you talking about?</i></b></font>

378
00:16:14,307 --> 00:16:15,775
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"We achieved
something together</i></b></font>

379
00:16:15,850 --> 00:16:18,649
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"that neither one of us
could have done on our own."</i></b></font>

380
00:16:21,105 --> 00:16:22,277
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Our sons.</i></b></font>

381
00:16:23,774 --> 00:16:25,447
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey and Marcus.</i></b></font>

382
00:16:26,068 --> 00:16:29,572
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>When Gordon was on the road,
he would call home.</i></b></font>

383
00:16:29,655 --> 00:16:31,657
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Six times a day
to check on them.</i></b></font>

384
00:16:31,741 --> 00:16:32,861
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"Did they eat enough dinner?</i></b></font>

385
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:35,583
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"Had they done homework?</i></b></font>

386
00:16:37,079 --> 00:16:39,582
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"How many points
did Marcus score?</i></b></font>

387
00:16:41,083 --> 00:16:43,427
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>"Did Harvey get his tux
for the prom?"</i></b></font>

388
00:16:44,754 --> 00:16:47,348
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Gordon was proud of a lot
of things in his life,</i></b></font>

389
00:16:47,423 --> 00:16:52,020
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but none of it compared
to how proud he was of them.</i></b></font>

390
00:16:54,222 --> 00:16:55,940
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They were his everything.</i></b></font>

391
00:16:59,143 --> 00:17:01,237
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And no matter where he is...</i></b></font>

392
00:17:03,147 --> 00:17:05,650
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know he is watching
over them right now.</i></b></font>

393
00:17:25,127 --> 00:17:27,425
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What are you doing here?
I'm doing my job.</i></b></font>

394
00:17:27,547 --> 00:17:29,720
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This is my case, not yours.
No, Marissa, it's our case.</i></b></font>

395
00:17:29,799 --> 00:17:30,800
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We're on the same side.</i></b></font>

396
00:17:30,883 --> 00:17:33,306
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And if you'd just listen to me,
you might learn something.</i></b></font>

397
00:17:33,469 --> 00:17:36,518
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Like what? Like the ways experienced
attorneys can trick you.</i></b></font>

398
00:17:36,597 --> 00:17:37,940
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not gonna get tricked.</i></b></font>

399
00:17:38,015 --> 00:17:39,767
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, if you don't mind, I'd
like to meet with my client.</i></b></font>

400
00:17:39,850 --> 00:17:41,102
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I've already met with her.</i></b></font>

401
00:17:41,477 --> 00:17:42,979
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You met her without me?</i></b></font>

402
00:17:43,479 --> 00:17:45,197
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>When did you do this?
A half hour ago.</i></b></font>

403
00:17:45,273 --> 00:17:46,913
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You said 3:00, so I
called her in at 2:30,</i></b></font>

404
00:17:46,941 --> 00:17:48,739
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>because I knew you wouldn't
give me the chance to meet her.</i></b></font>

405
00:17:48,818 --> 00:17:50,946
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Just like I know the other
side is gonna approach her</i></b></font>

406
00:17:51,028 --> 00:17:52,154
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>when you're not there.</i></b></font>

407
00:17:52,238 --> 00:17:53,330
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They can't do that.
Why?</i></b></font>

408
00:17:53,406 --> 00:17:55,408
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because it's unfair?
Because it's illegal.</i></b></font>

409
00:17:55,491 --> 00:17:57,289
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Only if she pursues them,
which she'll never do.</i></b></font>

410
00:17:57,368 --> 00:17:59,416
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because they're gonna find out
whatever her weak spots are</i></b></font>

411
00:17:59,495 --> 00:18:02,123
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and then they're gonna offer her exactly
the amount she needs to get by,</i></b></font>

412
00:18:02,206 --> 00:18:03,753
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and then
she's gonna take it.</i></b></font>

413
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,627
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If she does that,
she'll end up homeless.</i></b></font>

414
00:18:05,710 --> 00:18:08,133
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which is why we need to be
prepared for it to happen.</i></b></font>

415
00:18:08,838 --> 00:18:11,512
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Now, do you want to work on
this thing together or not?</i></b></font>

416
00:18:20,558 --> 00:18:24,188
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm sorry I didn't tell you that she was
going to speak before you got here.</i></b></font>

417
00:18:25,354 --> 00:18:27,448
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just didn't have it in me
to have it out with you.</i></b></font>

418
00:18:27,523 --> 00:18:28,820
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's okay, Marcus.</i></b></font>

419
00:18:31,694 --> 00:18:33,116
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She got to you,
didn't she?</i></b></font>

420
00:18:34,196 --> 00:18:35,789
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm sad about Dad.</i></b></font>

421
00:18:36,324 --> 00:18:39,123
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And, uh, yeah,
she pulled on that string.</i></b></font>

422
00:18:39,201 --> 00:18:42,000
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But one speech doesn't
make up for everything.</i></b></font>

423
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:44,502
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe it doesn't.</i></b></font>

424
00:18:45,333 --> 00:18:47,301
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But you have to
start somewhere.</i></b></font>

425
00:18:49,045 --> 00:18:51,047
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah. Well...</i></b></font>

426
00:18:52,632 --> 00:18:53,929
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm going to
head back home.</i></b></font>

427
00:18:54,008 --> 00:18:55,009
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, come on, Harvey.</i></b></font>

428
00:18:55,092 --> 00:18:56,844
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Come to the house
for the wake.</i></b></font>

429
00:18:57,928 --> 00:18:59,976
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I got a few things I got
to take care of at work.</i></b></font>

430
00:19:00,056 --> 00:19:01,182
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, come on, Harvey.</i></b></font>

431
00:19:01,265 --> 00:19:02,767
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're not leaving
because of work.</i></b></font>

432
00:19:07,730 --> 00:19:09,698
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's time to let things go.</i></b></font>

433
00:19:13,444 --> 00:19:16,243
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I complained about the heat
not working a million times.</i></b></font>

434
00:19:16,322 --> 00:19:19,075
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The landlord always says he's going
to fix it, and then nothing happens.</i></b></font>

435
00:19:19,158 --> 00:19:21,456
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We couldn't afford to move,
so I was just making do.</i></b></font>

436
00:19:21,535 --> 00:19:24,709
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But then, my little
guy, he got asthma.</i></b></font>

437
00:19:25,498 --> 00:19:29,469
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The doctor said that we need to
keep all of the windows shut,</i></b></font>

438
00:19:29,543 --> 00:19:30,795
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>keep out the pollution.</i></b></font>

439
00:19:30,878 --> 00:19:33,097
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But the window
in the living room,</i></b></font>

440
00:19:33,172 --> 00:19:35,095
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>it's been broken
for seven months.</i></b></font>

441
00:19:35,508 --> 00:19:37,351
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>My son is
only three years old.</i></b></font>

442
00:19:37,426 --> 00:19:39,349
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The sound of him
wheezing at night,</i></b></font>

443
00:19:40,262 --> 00:19:42,685
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>not knowing if he's gonna
wake up in the morning.</i></b></font>

444
00:19:43,015 --> 00:19:46,235
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, I thought, since that
slumlord only cares about money,</i></b></font>

445
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:49,860
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not gonna pay rent until he fixes
the window and turns on the heat.</i></b></font>

446
00:19:49,939 --> 00:19:53,034
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm so sorry, Sofia.
That sounds terrible.</i></b></font>

447
00:19:53,109 --> 00:19:54,156
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It is.</i></b></font>

448
00:19:54,819 --> 00:19:56,492
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And no one should
have to live like that.</i></b></font>

449
00:19:57,530 --> 00:20:00,579
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But by violating your lease,
he has grounds to evict you.</i></b></font>

450
00:20:00,658 --> 00:20:03,332
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which is why you have to give him
a check for the money you owe him</i></b></font>

451
00:20:03,411 --> 00:20:04,708
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>while this case
moves forward.</i></b></font>

452
00:20:04,787 --> 00:20:06,130
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I... I can't do that.</i></b></font>

453
00:20:06,414 --> 00:20:08,007
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You don't have
the money anymore.</i></b></font>

454
00:20:08,249 --> 00:20:11,048
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I had to buy blankets,
space heaters.</i></b></font>

455
00:20:11,127 --> 00:20:13,926
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>There were a couple of nights
that A.J.'s breathing was so bad,</i></b></font>

456
00:20:14,004 --> 00:20:16,006
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>we had to go to
a motel down the street.</i></b></font>

457
00:20:16,132 --> 00:20:17,384
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Don't worry, Sofia.</i></b></font>

458
00:20:17,466 --> 00:20:21,061
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Not only are we gonna get your
window fixed, but I promise you,</i></b></font>

459
00:20:21,137 --> 00:20:22,730
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you'll get to
keep your home, too.</i></b></font>

460
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:25,308
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thank you.</i></b></font>

461
00:20:35,609 --> 00:20:36,952
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Are you crazy?</i></b></font>

462
00:20:37,903 --> 00:20:39,780
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What are you talking about?
You just told her</i></b></font>

463
00:20:39,864 --> 00:20:40,831
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you were gonna
fix her problem.</i></b></font>

464
00:20:40,948 --> 00:20:42,950
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I'm going to fix her problem.
That's not the point.</i></b></font>

465
00:20:43,033 --> 00:20:44,831
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Even if you think you can
make everything better,</i></b></font>

466
00:20:44,910 --> 00:20:46,537
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you don't guarantee
that to a client.</i></b></font>

467
00:20:48,664 --> 00:20:49,836
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You know what?</i></b></font>

468
00:20:49,915 --> 00:20:52,589
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe you don't care about
these people, but I do.</i></b></font>

469
00:20:52,668 --> 00:20:53,794
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, my God.
And I'm willing to fight</i></b></font>

470
00:20:53,878 --> 00:20:55,004
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to make sure
they stay in their home</i></b></font>

471
00:20:55,045 --> 00:20:57,844
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I'm not afraid to tell her that.
This is not about caring.</i></b></font>

472
00:20:58,591 --> 00:21:00,093
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>There's a real world
out there.</i></b></font>

473
00:21:00,176 --> 00:21:01,894
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And like I told you,
there's an experienced lawyer</i></b></font>

474
00:21:01,969 --> 00:21:03,812
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>on the other side looking
to exploit our mistakes.</i></b></font>

475
00:21:03,888 --> 00:21:05,890
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If you over-promise
and under-deliver,</i></b></font>

476
00:21:05,973 --> 00:21:08,271
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you're just making them that much
more vulnerable to a shitty offer.</i></b></font>

477
00:21:08,350 --> 00:21:10,478
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Is that what they taught you
in corporate low-balling 101?</i></b></font>

478
00:21:10,561 --> 00:21:12,609
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Excuse me? You don't give a
shit about these people.</i></b></font>

479
00:21:12,730 --> 00:21:16,780
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And Nathan and everyone else here
might be buying your bullshit,</i></b></font>

480
00:21:16,859 --> 00:21:18,406
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I know
why you're really here.</i></b></font>

481
00:21:20,488 --> 00:21:21,580
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I get it.</i></b></font>

482
00:21:22,364 --> 00:21:23,490
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You checked up on me.</i></b></font>

483
00:21:23,574 --> 00:21:24,666
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I didn't need
to check up on you.</i></b></font>

484
00:21:24,742 --> 00:21:26,836
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I've heard your story
1,000 times.</i></b></font>

485
00:21:26,911 --> 00:21:28,458
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You couldn't hack it
at your corporate law firm.</i></b></font>

486
00:21:28,537 --> 00:21:29,880
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, you're slumming it here</i></b></font>

487
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:32,629
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>until you can figure out a way
to jump back into your cushy,</i></b></font>

488
00:21:32,708 --> 00:21:34,551
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>stick it
to the working man job.</i></b></font>

489
00:21:37,588 --> 00:21:38,885
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I see that I'm right.</i></b></font>

490
00:21:39,715 --> 00:21:42,685
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, keep your wisdom
to yourself.</i></b></font>

491
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:45,309
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I'm actually here
to help people,</i></b></font>

492
00:21:45,387 --> 00:21:48,311
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Not just remind them what a
cruel world it is out there.</i></b></font>

493
00:21:55,356 --> 00:21:56,733
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey Specter's office.</i></b></font>

494
00:21:56,899 --> 00:21:58,151
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Donna, it's me.</i></b></font>

495
00:21:58,984 --> 00:22:00,236
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, hey.</i></b></font>

496
00:22:00,569 --> 00:22:03,197
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Are you almost here? Because your
6:00 is in the conference room.</i></b></font>

497
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:05,032
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not back
in New York yet.</i></b></font>

498
00:22:05,199 --> 00:22:06,291
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You were right, Donna.</i></b></font>

499
00:22:06,408 --> 00:22:07,409
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>About what?</i></b></font>

500
00:22:08,410 --> 00:22:11,584
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If I'd missed his funeral, I never
would be able to forgive myself.</i></b></font>

501
00:22:14,875 --> 00:22:16,548
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Good luck making up
with your mom.</i></b></font>

502
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,012
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How did you know?</i></b></font>

503
00:22:19,088 --> 00:22:20,681
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because you've never
missed a flight</i></b></font>

504
00:22:20,756 --> 00:22:22,224
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>in your entire life.</i></b></font>

505
00:22:22,299 --> 00:22:23,846
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And the only reason
you'd stay longer</i></b></font>

506
00:22:23,926 --> 00:22:26,770
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>is if things are going better
than you thought they would.</i></b></font>

507
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:29,432
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thanks, Donna.</i></b></font>

508
00:22:29,515 --> 00:22:31,062
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't need
your thanks, Harvey.</i></b></font>

509
00:22:31,141 --> 00:22:32,939
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm just really happy
you're there.</i></b></font>

510
00:22:42,444 --> 00:22:43,866
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know
what you're thinking.</i></b></font>

511
00:22:43,946 --> 00:22:45,163
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How could she not know?</i></b></font>

512
00:22:45,990 --> 00:22:47,788
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I checked the box.
You did.</i></b></font>

513
00:22:47,867 --> 00:22:50,211
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I was the one who brought
the application to Nathan</i></b></font>

514
00:22:50,286 --> 00:22:51,788
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and he told me
not to tell anyone.</i></b></font>

515
00:22:52,037 --> 00:22:53,038
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Why not?</i></b></font>

516
00:22:53,122 --> 00:22:54,874
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because he didn't
want them to judge you.</i></b></font>

517
00:22:55,124 --> 00:22:57,172
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I would have thought
everyone knew, anyway.</i></b></font>

518
00:22:57,585 --> 00:22:59,053
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Why would you
think that?</i></b></font>

519
00:22:59,628 --> 00:23:01,130
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because it was
all over The Journal.</i></b></font>

520
00:23:01,213 --> 00:23:03,557
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>People here don't
read The Journal.</i></b></font>

521
00:23:03,632 --> 00:23:05,179
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We read
The Huffington Post.</i></b></font>

522
00:23:06,969 --> 00:23:09,518
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, what Marissa thinks is what
they all think. I don't know.</i></b></font>

523
00:23:09,597 --> 00:23:10,769
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But for what it's worth,</i></b></font>

524
00:23:10,848 --> 00:23:13,476
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I wouldn't have said anything
whether Nathan told me to or not.</i></b></font>

525
00:23:14,935 --> 00:23:16,278
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's not my story
to tell.</i></b></font>

526
00:23:16,812 --> 00:23:17,904
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thank you, Oliver.</i></b></font>

527
00:23:18,439 --> 00:23:19,486
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah.</i></b></font>

528
00:23:55,184 --> 00:23:56,936
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You made
your strawberry pie.</i></b></font>

529
00:23:58,437 --> 00:23:59,859
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It was his favorite.</i></b></font>

530
00:24:00,606 --> 00:24:02,529
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe you forgot
it was mine, too.</i></b></font>

531
00:24:03,025 --> 00:24:04,277
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I didn't forget.</i></b></font>

532
00:24:07,488 --> 00:24:08,990
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It was a nice speech.</i></b></font>

533
00:24:09,907 --> 00:24:11,375
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thank you, Harvey.</i></b></font>

534
00:24:15,037 --> 00:24:16,254
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey.</i></b></font>

535
00:24:17,790 --> 00:24:19,042
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>When my parents died,</i></b></font>

536
00:24:19,124 --> 00:24:22,173
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I felt like I was completely
alone in the world.</i></b></font>

537
00:24:22,836 --> 00:24:24,554
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't want you
to feel that way.</i></b></font>

538
00:24:24,922 --> 00:24:26,219
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I want you to know</i></b></font>

539
00:24:27,007 --> 00:24:29,556
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that whether you want me
in your life or not,</i></b></font>

540
00:24:30,511 --> 00:24:32,684
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you still have a mother
that loves you</i></b></font>

541
00:24:33,847 --> 00:24:35,815
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and will always
be there for you.</i></b></font>

542
00:24:38,477 --> 00:24:39,603
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know that.</i></b></font>

543
00:24:43,315 --> 00:24:44,441
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, I'm...</i></b></font>

544
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:46,493
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm sorry for your loss.</i></b></font>

545
00:24:49,363 --> 00:24:50,706
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Are you kidding me?</i></b></font>

546
00:24:51,031 --> 00:24:53,079
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You brought him here?
Harvey...</i></b></font>

547
00:24:53,492 --> 00:24:55,212
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I said you have the nerve
to bring him here?</i></b></font>

548
00:24:55,244 --> 00:24:57,292
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He's my partner. Is that what you
call every guy you slept with</i></b></font>

549
00:24:57,371 --> 00:24:58,497
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>while you were with Dad?</i></b></font>

550
00:24:58,580 --> 00:24:59,832
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Don't speak to me
like that.</i></b></font>

551
00:24:59,915 --> 00:25:01,713
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Bobby and I
are still together.</i></b></font>

552
00:25:01,792 --> 00:25:03,840
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>- You think I give a shit?
- You should,</i></b></font>

553
00:25:03,919 --> 00:25:05,512
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>because it shows
what kind of man I am.</i></b></font>

554
00:25:05,587 --> 00:25:06,588
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're a piece of shit.</i></b></font>

555
00:25:06,672 --> 00:25:09,801
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You have no right being here the day
we put my father in the ground.</i></b></font>

556
00:25:09,883 --> 00:25:12,432
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, please.
We were just about...</i></b></font>

557
00:25:12,511 --> 00:25:14,231
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, I don't care
what we were about to do.</i></b></font>

558
00:25:14,304 --> 00:25:16,306
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You spit in Dad's face
by bringing him here.</i></b></font>

559
00:25:16,390 --> 00:25:18,108
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's okay, Lily.
I'll go.</i></b></font>

560
00:25:18,183 --> 00:25:19,623
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't care
whether you stay or not.</i></b></font>

561
00:25:19,685 --> 00:25:21,062
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, well, I do.</i></b></font>

562
00:25:21,145 --> 00:25:23,147
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And he is staying.</i></b></font>

563
00:25:23,230 --> 00:25:24,732
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because you may not
want to hear this,</i></b></font>

564
00:25:24,815 --> 00:25:27,364
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but your father accepted
him a long time ago.</i></b></font>

565
00:25:27,443 --> 00:25:28,945
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You know what? You want
to take his place, Bobby?</i></b></font>

566
00:25:29,028 --> 00:25:30,029
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Why don't you go
right ahead?</i></b></font>

567
00:25:30,112 --> 00:25:32,661
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe one day, you'll even walk
in on her with another guy</i></b></font>

568
00:25:32,740 --> 00:25:35,084
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and you'll know exactly
what my father felt.</i></b></font>

569
00:25:35,159 --> 00:25:37,457
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The only difference will be
at least then,</i></b></font>

570
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:40,623
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I won't be asked to keep
the goddamn secret.</i></b></font>

571
00:25:51,967 --> 00:25:53,469
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, what's good here?</i></b></font>

572
00:25:53,802 --> 00:25:55,645
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Actually,
everything's good here.</i></b></font>

573
00:25:56,263 --> 00:25:57,560
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You eat here a lot?</i></b></font>

574
00:25:58,223 --> 00:25:59,475
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Of course I do.</i></b></font>

575
00:26:05,397 --> 00:26:06,819
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This...</i></b></font>

576
00:26:09,026 --> 00:26:10,824
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This feels strange,
doesn't it?</i></b></font>

577
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:12,537
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, a little bit.</i></b></font>

578
00:26:13,238 --> 00:26:14,285
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So...</i></b></font>

579
00:26:14,490 --> 00:26:15,867
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Where do we start?</i></b></font>

580
00:26:19,995 --> 00:26:23,841
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I guess we start with me telling
you that I'm ready to forgive you.</i></b></font>

581
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:28,052
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Why now?</i></b></font>

582
00:26:28,796 --> 00:26:32,426
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Someone very special to me
convinced me that I needed to.</i></b></font>

583
00:26:33,383 --> 00:26:34,680
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Whoever it is,</i></b></font>

584
00:26:36,512 --> 00:26:37,980
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm glad she did.</i></b></font>

585
00:26:39,348 --> 00:26:40,440
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's good.</i></b></font>

586
00:26:41,266 --> 00:26:42,609
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I want you to know</i></b></font>

587
00:26:43,102 --> 00:26:44,729
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that I forgive you, too.</i></b></font>

588
00:26:46,647 --> 00:26:48,240
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Forgive me for what?</i></b></font>

589
00:26:48,315 --> 00:26:49,612
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>For the last time
I saw you.</i></b></font>

590
00:26:49,691 --> 00:26:51,113
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And for you being
gone all those years.</i></b></font>

591
00:26:51,193 --> 00:26:52,490
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I had my reasons to be gone.</i></b></font>

592
00:26:52,569 --> 00:26:54,617
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes. You did
when you were younger.</i></b></font>

593
00:26:54,696 --> 00:26:56,118
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But you're not
a child anymore,</i></b></font>

594
00:26:56,198 --> 00:26:57,871
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and you haven't been
for a long time.</i></b></font>

595
00:26:58,367 --> 00:27:00,870
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can't believe you. You're
turning this around on me?</i></b></font>

596
00:27:00,953 --> 00:27:03,627
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not turning it
around, Harvey.</i></b></font>

597
00:27:04,665 --> 00:27:07,635
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You have no idea what
it's like to have a child</i></b></font>

598
00:27:07,709 --> 00:27:10,132
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>who acts like
you don't even exist.</i></b></font>

599
00:27:10,212 --> 00:27:11,805
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And you don't know what
it's like to have a mother</i></b></font>

600
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:14,554
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>who asks you to lie to
his own father for her.</i></b></font>

601
00:27:15,217 --> 00:27:17,311
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, I never
should have done that.</i></b></font>

602
00:27:17,386 --> 00:27:18,808
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I have been
trying to tell you</i></b></font>

603
00:27:18,887 --> 00:27:21,231
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I am sorry about it
for 20 years.</i></b></font>

604
00:27:21,348 --> 00:27:22,600
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But until yesterday,</i></b></font>

605
00:27:22,683 --> 00:27:26,438
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you made it clear to me that you had no
interest in whether I lived or died.</i></b></font>

606
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:27,567
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I didn't.</i></b></font>

607
00:27:27,646 --> 00:27:29,239
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, can't you understand</i></b></font>

608
00:27:29,314 --> 00:27:31,658
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>how that could
devastate a person?</i></b></font>

609
00:27:31,733 --> 00:27:34,361
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can understand
how this was just a mistake.</i></b></font>

610
00:27:34,778 --> 00:27:36,325
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because you are
the same selfish,</i></b></font>

611
00:27:36,405 --> 00:27:38,533
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>self-centered, disloyal
woman you always were.</i></b></font>

612
00:27:38,615 --> 00:27:40,333
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And you are the same
self-absorbed,</i></b></font>

613
00:27:40,409 --> 00:27:42,662
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>childish man
you always were.</i></b></font>

614
00:27:42,744 --> 00:27:44,041
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, whose fault is that?</i></b></font>

615
00:27:44,121 --> 00:27:45,748
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, there you go.
Leave.</i></b></font>

616
00:27:46,123 --> 00:27:48,251
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's what you do best.
What did you just say to me?</i></b></font>

617
00:27:48,333 --> 00:27:50,051
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I said take a look
in the mirror, Harvey.</i></b></font>

618
00:27:50,127 --> 00:27:52,721
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I may have neglected
my family in the past,</i></b></font>

619
00:27:52,796 --> 00:27:55,845
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but you've been doing it
for as long as I can remember.</i></b></font>

620
00:28:15,819 --> 00:28:18,368
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, what am I supposed to
tell the kids in the morning?</i></b></font>

621
00:28:18,447 --> 00:28:20,620
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You tell them I've got
business back in New York.</i></b></font>

622
00:28:21,283 --> 00:28:22,500
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You want me to lie for you.</i></b></font>

623
00:28:22,618 --> 00:28:23,618
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>God damn it, Marcus,</i></b></font>

624
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:26,709
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>she had the nerve to say
that I owed her an apology.</i></b></font>

625
00:28:28,123 --> 00:28:30,217
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If that's her, you tell her
I've got nothing more to say.</i></b></font>

626
00:28:30,292 --> 00:28:32,212
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You know what, Harvey?
You can tell her yourself.</i></b></font>

627
00:28:32,252 --> 00:28:34,596
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I'm done being
in the middle of you two.</i></b></font>

628
00:28:37,966 --> 00:28:39,183
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>- Bobby.
- Where is he?</i></b></font>

629
00:28:39,259 --> 00:28:41,557
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey, now's not the time to...
Why, you son of a bitch.</i></b></font>

630
00:28:41,637 --> 00:28:43,264
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You think you can just
walk into our lives, and...</i></b></font>

631
00:28:43,347 --> 00:28:45,896
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And rip open old wounds?
Your lives?</i></b></font>

632
00:28:45,974 --> 00:28:48,944
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You better get the hell out of my face
before I do something that you'll regret.</i></b></font>

633
00:28:49,019 --> 00:28:51,898
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You already did something I regret by
talking to your mother the way you did.</i></b></font>

634
00:28:51,980 --> 00:28:54,403
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That woman gave up the right
to be called my mother</i></b></font>

635
00:28:54,483 --> 00:28:56,485
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>when she got together with
you behind my father's back.</i></b></font>

636
00:28:56,568 --> 00:28:58,946
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, maybe you don't consider
her to be your mother.</i></b></font>

637
00:28:59,029 --> 00:29:00,121
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But she's my wife.</i></b></font>

638
00:29:00,197 --> 00:29:01,949
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And if anyone else spoke
to her the way you did,</i></b></font>

639
00:29:02,032 --> 00:29:03,312
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>they'd be on the floor
right now.</i></b></font>

640
00:29:03,325 --> 00:29:04,622
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>- You want to take a swing at me?
- Harvey.</i></b></font>

641
00:29:04,701 --> 00:29:06,781
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey. No, no, no. Let him
get it out of his system.</i></b></font>

642
00:29:06,828 --> 00:29:08,956
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I know I want
to get it out of mine.</i></b></font>

643
00:29:10,332 --> 00:29:12,209
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I didn't come here
to fight, Harvey.</i></b></font>

644
00:29:13,418 --> 00:29:16,422
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I came here to tell you I've never
seen your mother more excited</i></b></font>

645
00:29:16,505 --> 00:29:18,678
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>than when she was heading out
to have dinner with you.</i></b></font>

646
00:29:19,466 --> 00:29:22,219
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She was finally gonna get
to reconnect with her son.</i></b></font>

647
00:29:22,302 --> 00:29:24,100
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And then you pulled the rug
out from underneath her.</i></b></font>

648
00:29:24,179 --> 00:29:25,931
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You took that
excitement away.</i></b></font>

649
00:29:26,014 --> 00:29:29,018
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, when you leave this time, just
stay gone. Because the truth is,</i></b></font>

650
00:29:30,185 --> 00:29:32,233
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>this family works better
without you.</i></b></font>

651
00:29:40,737 --> 00:29:41,954
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, I need you
to help me with something</i></b></font>

652
00:29:42,030 --> 00:29:43,350
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I need it quickly.
What is it?</i></b></font>

653
00:29:43,365 --> 00:29:45,709
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Teddy Doyle
needs to access the proceeds</i></b></font>

654
00:29:45,784 --> 00:29:48,537
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>from the sale of his company that
were put in trust to avoid taxes,</i></b></font>

655
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:50,793
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and he needs to do it without
triggering those taxes.</i></b></font>

656
00:29:50,872 --> 00:29:51,998
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Louis,
are you kidding?</i></b></font>

657
00:29:52,082 --> 00:29:53,202
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This isn't Dubai.</i></b></font>

658
00:29:53,208 --> 00:29:54,380
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He's not gonna be
able to do that.</i></b></font>

659
00:29:54,459 --> 00:29:56,837
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I know that. But I need him
to be able to, anyway.</i></b></font>

660
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,803
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Give me the file.
I'll figure something out.</i></b></font>

661
00:30:00,882 --> 00:30:01,883
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thanks.</i></b></font>

662
00:30:01,967 --> 00:30:03,139
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm proud of you,
Louis.</i></b></font>

663
00:30:04,761 --> 00:30:07,059
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>For what? Teddy Doyle
is Harvey's client.</i></b></font>

664
00:30:07,264 --> 00:30:09,016
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I heard
about your thing.</i></b></font>

665
00:30:09,099 --> 00:30:11,352
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, this must mean
that you forgave him.</i></b></font>

666
00:30:12,269 --> 00:30:13,486
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I did.</i></b></font>

667
00:30:14,563 --> 00:30:16,736
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Bring that to me as soon
as you have something.</i></b></font>

668
00:30:22,487 --> 00:30:24,831
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey, Mike, I've got a question
about the Haberman case.</i></b></font>

669
00:30:24,906 --> 00:30:26,749
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He lost his job. They're taking his car.
I'm trying...</i></b></font>

670
00:30:26,825 --> 00:30:28,543
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You need
a reaffirmation agreement.</i></b></font>

671
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:29,832
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Can I help you in a minute?
Yeah.</i></b></font>

672
00:30:29,911 --> 00:30:30,912
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Great.</i></b></font>

673
00:30:34,666 --> 00:30:36,760
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey, everyone, can you
listen up for a sec?</i></b></font>

674
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:39,921
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Marissa.</i></b></font>

675
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:43,137
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This won't take long.</i></b></font>

676
00:30:45,260 --> 00:30:46,432
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>When Nathan introduced me,</i></b></font>

677
00:30:46,511 --> 00:30:49,014
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>he told you that I used to
work at Pearson Specter Litt.</i></b></font>

678
00:30:49,264 --> 00:30:52,268
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What he didn't tell you is why
I don't work there anymore.</i></b></font>

679
00:30:53,268 --> 00:30:56,738
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And the reason isn't that I couldn't
hack it as a corporate lawyer.</i></b></font>

680
00:30:57,773 --> 00:30:59,946
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's because
I wasn't a lawyer at all.</i></b></font>

681
00:31:02,944 --> 00:31:04,537
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Here. Read that.</i></b></font>

682
00:31:07,157 --> 00:31:08,909
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That is my story.</i></b></font>

683
00:31:08,992 --> 00:31:10,289
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's what I did.</i></b></font>

684
00:31:10,952 --> 00:31:12,920
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Every word
of these articles is true.</i></b></font>

685
00:31:15,415 --> 00:31:17,759
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I never should have been
at Pearson Specter.</i></b></font>

686
00:31:19,628 --> 00:31:23,098
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But not being a lawyer isn't the
only reason I didn't belong there.</i></b></font>

687
00:31:23,507 --> 00:31:27,102
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You see, the whole reason that I wanted
to be a lawyer in the first place</i></b></font>

688
00:31:27,177 --> 00:31:29,430
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>was so that I could help the kind of
people that come into this clinic</i></b></font>

689
00:31:29,513 --> 00:31:30,765
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>every single day.</i></b></font>

690
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:33,266
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Now, I thought
you all knew this,</i></b></font>

691
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:35,444
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but it's clear to me now
that you don't.</i></b></font>

692
00:31:35,977 --> 00:31:38,400
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Now, Nathan wanted
to protect me.</i></b></font>

693
00:31:39,314 --> 00:31:40,361
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But...</i></b></font>

694
00:31:41,775 --> 00:31:43,448
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'd rather have you
respect me.</i></b></font>

695
00:31:44,736 --> 00:31:46,296
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If any of you have
any questions at all,</i></b></font>

696
00:31:46,363 --> 00:31:48,741
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>please come talk to me
about it. But if not,</i></b></font>

697
00:31:48,824 --> 00:31:50,326
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>let's get back to work.</i></b></font>

698
00:31:54,371 --> 00:31:55,668
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mike.</i></b></font>

699
00:31:57,165 --> 00:31:58,712
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You didn't
have to do that.</i></b></font>

700
00:32:01,211 --> 00:32:02,463
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, I did.</i></b></font>

701
00:32:09,845 --> 00:32:11,017
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey.</i></b></font>

702
00:32:12,097 --> 00:32:13,189
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're still here.</i></b></font>

703
00:32:13,348 --> 00:32:15,646
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>My flight isn't for
another two hours.</i></b></font>

704
00:32:16,518 --> 00:32:18,646
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I wasn't gonna let that
asshole drive me away.</i></b></font>

705
00:32:18,728 --> 00:32:20,150
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Listen, Harvey,</i></b></font>

706
00:32:20,355 --> 00:32:22,278
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>about what Bobby
said last night?</i></b></font>

707
00:32:22,357 --> 00:32:23,779
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You don't need to make
excuses for him, Marcus.</i></b></font>

708
00:32:23,859 --> 00:32:25,736
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, I'm not
making excuses.</i></b></font>

709
00:32:25,819 --> 00:32:28,299
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I am telling you he had every right
to say what he said to you.</i></b></font>

710
00:32:28,363 --> 00:32:30,123
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't believe this.
You're on his side now?</i></b></font>

711
00:32:30,157 --> 00:32:31,875
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The only side I'm on
is my family's.</i></b></font>

712
00:32:31,950 --> 00:32:33,452
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The family that you've
never been a part of.</i></b></font>

713
00:32:33,535 --> 00:32:34,752
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Marcus, come on.</i></b></font>

714
00:32:34,828 --> 00:32:37,047
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Do you know what it's like
to tell a 5-year-old</i></b></font>

715
00:32:37,122 --> 00:32:40,296
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>why Grandma and Uncle Harvey can't
be in the same room together?</i></b></font>

716
00:32:40,375 --> 00:32:42,594
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because that's the position
you put me in.</i></b></font>

717
00:32:42,669 --> 00:32:44,091
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Year after year.</i></b></font>

718
00:32:44,171 --> 00:32:48,347
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>There's a whole life going on here
that you're not even a part of.</i></b></font>

719
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:49,802
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You think I don't know
what I've missed?</i></b></font>

720
00:32:49,885 --> 00:32:52,388
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not just talking
about birthdays, Harvey.</i></b></font>

721
00:32:58,727 --> 00:33:01,651
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I got sick again,
a couple of years ago.</i></b></font>

722
00:33:01,730 --> 00:33:02,731
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What?</i></b></font>

723
00:33:04,274 --> 00:33:06,322
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Why didn't you tell me?
Why would I?</i></b></font>

724
00:33:06,401 --> 00:33:08,654
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So that we could have this
at the same time?</i></b></font>

725
00:33:08,737 --> 00:33:10,330
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Marcus.
No, listen to me.</i></b></font>

726
00:33:10,405 --> 00:33:14,626
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You know who helped out when
Katie was taking me to chemo?</i></b></font>

727
00:33:14,701 --> 00:33:17,204
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mom made dinner
every night.</i></b></font>

728
00:33:17,287 --> 00:33:20,587
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Bobby took my kids
to school every day.</i></b></font>

729
00:33:20,665 --> 00:33:25,637
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Which means, while they
might be monsters to you.</i></b></font>

730
00:33:25,754 --> 00:33:27,176
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>To my kids,</i></b></font>

731
00:33:27,255 --> 00:33:30,099
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>they're Grandma
and Grandpa.</i></b></font>

732
00:33:30,842 --> 00:33:33,595
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And you might not have liked
that shit coming from Bobby,</i></b></font>

733
00:33:33,762 --> 00:33:35,435
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but it's the truth, Harvey.</i></b></font>

734
00:33:36,306 --> 00:33:38,104
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Whether you want
to hear it or not.</i></b></font>

735
00:33:45,190 --> 00:33:46,533
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Do you
have a minute?</i></b></font>

736
00:33:47,484 --> 00:33:48,610
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Of course.</i></b></font>

737
00:33:49,486 --> 00:33:51,113
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm sorry that
I misjudged you.</i></b></font>

738
00:33:51,947 --> 00:33:53,073
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's okay.</i></b></font>

739
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:56,243
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Like I said, we're on the same team.
We are.</i></b></font>

740
00:33:56,785 --> 00:33:59,584
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I also should not have
promised Sofia that we would win.</i></b></font>

741
00:33:59,663 --> 00:34:01,131
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I told you that
I wouldn't stop looking</i></b></font>

742
00:34:01,206 --> 00:34:02,332
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>for a way to keep her
in her home,</i></b></font>

743
00:34:02,415 --> 00:34:03,883
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I think I found one.</i></b></font>

744
00:34:03,959 --> 00:34:06,553
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Marissa, it doesn't matter what
kind of legal basis you've got.</i></b></font>

745
00:34:06,628 --> 00:34:08,380
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If she can't pay her rent
in the meantime, then...</i></b></font>

746
00:34:08,463 --> 00:34:09,623
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's what
I'm talking about.</i></b></font>

747
00:34:09,673 --> 00:34:10,720
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Troy v. Suffolk.</i></b></font>

748
00:34:10,799 --> 00:34:13,222
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>As long we can prove that she tried
to tell the landlord about the heat.</i></b></font>

749
00:34:13,301 --> 00:34:14,598
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, but we can't prove it.</i></b></font>

750
00:34:14,678 --> 00:34:15,975
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She doesn't have it
in writing.</i></b></font>

751
00:34:16,137 --> 00:34:17,730
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We can if we use
the phone records.</i></b></font>

752
00:34:17,806 --> 00:34:19,524
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Phone records
aren't proof of a complaint.</i></b></font>

753
00:34:20,141 --> 00:34:21,984
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, but the only people
who call their landlord</i></b></font>

754
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:23,562
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>three times a week
for two months</i></b></font>

755
00:34:23,645 --> 00:34:25,773
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>are people who have a
problem that needs fixing.</i></b></font>

756
00:34:29,276 --> 00:34:30,744
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then we enter
the motel receipts</i></b></font>

757
00:34:30,819 --> 00:34:32,116
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and the receipts
for the space heaters</i></b></font>

758
00:34:32,195 --> 00:34:33,913
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>as substitution
for rent paid.</i></b></font>

759
00:34:33,989 --> 00:34:35,662
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And not only
can he not evict her,</i></b></font>

760
00:34:35,740 --> 00:34:37,242
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>she doesn't have
to pay back rent.</i></b></font>

761
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:41,220
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We just need to convince the court
to accept these phone records.</i></b></font>

762
00:34:41,288 --> 00:34:43,632
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The problem is, we can't
convince the court of anything.</i></b></font>

763
00:34:43,707 --> 00:34:45,129
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not a lawyer yet.</i></b></font>

764
00:34:45,208 --> 00:34:47,210
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I was hoping you
could do it, but then...</i></b></font>

765
00:34:47,294 --> 00:34:48,295
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's okay.</i></b></font>

766
00:34:48,837 --> 00:34:50,339
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I've got just the person.</i></b></font>

767
00:34:55,010 --> 00:34:56,227
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey.</i></b></font>

768
00:34:56,678 --> 00:34:57,725
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Can I come in?</i></b></font>

769
00:34:57,846 --> 00:34:59,519
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Depends on why you're here.</i></b></font>

770
00:35:01,057 --> 00:35:03,810
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm here to apologize for
the way I acted last night.</i></b></font>

771
00:35:03,935 --> 00:35:06,438
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Is this 'cause Bobby
came to see you? No.</i></b></font>

772
00:35:06,521 --> 00:35:08,194
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's because
Marcus got sick</i></b></font>

773
00:35:08,273 --> 00:35:10,742
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and you took care of him and
he couldn't even tell me that.</i></b></font>

774
00:35:10,817 --> 00:35:12,444
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey...
I'm so angry.</i></b></font>

775
00:35:12,694 --> 00:35:13,946
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't wanna be
angry anymore,</i></b></font>

776
00:35:14,029 --> 00:35:15,326
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I don't know
how to stop.</i></b></font>

777
00:35:15,405 --> 00:35:20,127
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then let me say how sorry I am for all
the pain that I have caused you.</i></b></font>

778
00:35:20,201 --> 00:35:21,953
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You don't need to tell me
how sorry you are.</i></b></font>

779
00:35:22,037 --> 00:35:23,584
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes, I do.</i></b></font>

780
00:35:23,997 --> 00:35:28,969
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, we both may have played
a part in the last 20 years.</i></b></font>

781
00:35:29,377 --> 00:35:30,970
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I was an adult</i></b></font>

782
00:35:31,379 --> 00:35:33,677
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and I put you
in that position.</i></b></font>

783
00:35:34,257 --> 00:35:39,639
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And not a day goes by that I don't
understand why you hate me.</i></b></font>

784
00:35:39,846 --> 00:35:41,519
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was your mother.</i></b></font>

785
00:35:42,474 --> 00:35:44,852
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was
supposed to protect you,</i></b></font>

786
00:35:46,144 --> 00:35:47,612
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>not scar you.</i></b></font>

787
00:35:49,522 --> 00:35:50,694
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey...</i></b></font>

788
00:35:51,066 --> 00:35:54,161
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I am so sorry.</i></b></font>

789
00:35:57,572 --> 00:35:59,324
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't hate you, Morn.</i></b></font>

790
00:36:01,534 --> 00:36:05,209
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I hate what you did,
and I probably always will.</i></b></font>

791
00:36:05,830 --> 00:36:07,457
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I don't hate you.</i></b></font>

792
00:36:10,168 --> 00:36:11,511
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'll take that.</i></b></font>

793
00:36:16,841 --> 00:36:18,093
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What is it?</i></b></font>

794
00:36:18,718 --> 00:36:20,186
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's nothing. It's...</i></b></font>

795
00:36:21,930 --> 00:36:24,370
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's just I had your painting on
my wall for the longest time.</i></b></font>

796
00:36:24,432 --> 00:36:25,809
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I just realized...</i></b></font>

797
00:36:28,186 --> 00:36:29,779
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How much I missed it.</i></b></font>

798
00:36:32,148 --> 00:36:33,900
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I love you, Harvey.</i></b></font>

799
00:36:37,278 --> 00:36:38,780
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I love you, too, Morn.</i></b></font>

800
00:36:49,958 --> 00:36:53,087
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Your Honor, my client is a single
mother with two small children.</i></b></font>

801
00:36:53,169 --> 00:36:55,217
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And my dog is
a Labrador Retriever.</i></b></font>

802
00:36:55,296 --> 00:36:57,048
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But the only thing
that's relevant here</i></b></font>

803
00:36:57,132 --> 00:36:59,476
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>is that his client hasn't paid
her rent in three months.</i></b></font>

804
00:36:59,551 --> 00:37:01,895
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And the reason she hasn't paid
it is because she's had no heat</i></b></font>

805
00:37:01,970 --> 00:37:03,472
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and a broken window
all winter,</i></b></font>

806
00:37:03,555 --> 00:37:05,398
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>despite repeated requests
for repairs.</i></b></font>

807
00:37:05,473 --> 00:37:06,873
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>There is absolutely
no documentation</i></b></font>

808
00:37:06,891 --> 00:37:08,564
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>- of any such requests.
- That's not true.</i></b></font>

809
00:37:08,643 --> 00:37:11,817
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>My client called her landlord 20
times over the course of two months,</i></b></font>

810
00:37:11,896 --> 00:37:13,398
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>as you can see from
her phone records.</i></b></font>

811
00:37:13,481 --> 00:37:14,858
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's not
proof of anything.</i></b></font>

812
00:37:14,941 --> 00:37:17,785
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's proof your client spoke to mine for
an average of two minutes per call,</i></b></font>

813
00:37:17,861 --> 00:37:19,829
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and it wasn't to talk
about the weather.</i></b></font>

814
00:37:20,321 --> 00:37:21,743
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Your Honor,
Mr. Grady gave me</i></b></font>

815
00:37:21,823 --> 00:37:23,621
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>a copy of this nonsense
20 minutes ago</i></b></font>

816
00:37:23,700 --> 00:37:26,169
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and he specifically agreed
it wasn't relevant.</i></b></font>

817
00:37:26,286 --> 00:37:27,913
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That... That is a lie. Really?</i></b></font>

818
00:37:27,996 --> 00:37:30,875
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because I have a phone
record of a two-minute call</i></b></font>

819
00:37:30,957 --> 00:37:34,302
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that I made to you
10 minutes ago.</i></b></font>

820
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,092
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You may have called me,</i></b></font>

821
00:37:37,172 --> 00:37:38,424
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but we didn't talk
about that.</i></b></font>

822
00:37:38,506 --> 00:37:39,632
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's right.</i></b></font>

823
00:37:39,716 --> 00:37:43,311
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Just because I called you doesn't mean
I can prove what we talked about.</i></b></font>

824
00:37:44,512 --> 00:37:46,606
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Your Honor,
she called 20 times.</i></b></font>

825
00:37:46,681 --> 00:37:48,228
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, probably to
say why her rent was late,</i></b></font>

826
00:37:48,308 --> 00:37:49,685
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>because she never paid it.</i></b></font>

827
00:37:49,768 --> 00:37:52,612
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But we won't know that because
we don't have it in writing,</i></b></font>

828
00:37:52,687 --> 00:37:54,860
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>which is what
the court requires.</i></b></font>

829
00:37:55,648 --> 00:37:56,808
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Your Honor, I need...</i></b></font>

830
00:37:57,358 --> 00:37:59,656
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'd like to request time
to confer with my supervisor.</i></b></font>

831
00:37:59,736 --> 00:38:02,330
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>His supervisor?
He's a lawyer.</i></b></font>

832
00:38:02,447 --> 00:38:03,744
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You have to help him.
I can't.</i></b></font>

833
00:38:03,823 --> 00:38:06,167
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just need a minute to..-
To gather my thoughts.</i></b></font>

834
00:38:06,242 --> 00:38:07,334
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What is this,
pre-school circle time?</i></b></font>

835
00:38:07,410 --> 00:38:09,629
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Your Honor, the woman
didn't pay her rent.</i></b></font>

836
00:38:09,704 --> 00:38:10,830
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The deadline is now.</i></b></font>

837
00:38:10,914 --> 00:38:12,837
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We are requesting
permission to evict</i></b></font>

838
00:38:12,916 --> 00:38:15,419
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>if we don't have a check
by 10:00 a.m. tomorrow.</i></b></font>

839
00:38:15,502 --> 00:38:16,542
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Your Honor, please.</i></b></font>

840
00:38:16,586 --> 00:38:18,026
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She's gonna lose her home.</i></b></font>

841
00:38:19,088 --> 00:38:20,385
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Time's up, Counselor.</i></b></font>

842
00:38:20,465 --> 00:38:22,308
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Permission granted.</i></b></font>

843
00:38:32,977 --> 00:38:34,524
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, what are you
doing here?</i></b></font>

844
00:38:34,771 --> 00:38:35,897
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>When did you get back?</i></b></font>

845
00:38:36,231 --> 00:38:37,403
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Ten minutes ago.</i></b></font>

846
00:38:38,691 --> 00:38:39,863
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How did it go?</i></b></font>

847
00:38:40,735 --> 00:38:41,987
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It went well.</i></b></font>

848
00:38:44,531 --> 00:38:45,623
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm glad.</i></b></font>

849
00:38:48,743 --> 00:38:50,165
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>As a matter of fact,</i></b></font>

850
00:38:50,245 --> 00:38:51,497
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I need your help
with something.</i></b></font>

851
00:38:51,579 --> 00:38:52,580
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Anything.</i></b></font>

852
00:38:53,081 --> 00:38:54,924
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But there's something
you have to do first.</i></b></font>

853
00:38:58,169 --> 00:38:59,170
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mr. Ross.</i></b></font>

854
00:38:59,254 --> 00:39:01,723
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Ms. Price, I wanted to talk to you.
Do you have a minute?</i></b></font>

855
00:39:01,798 --> 00:39:03,015
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Not really.</i></b></font>

856
00:39:03,258 --> 00:39:04,510
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They're coming tomorrow.</i></b></font>

857
00:39:04,592 --> 00:39:06,765
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I've been packing and...
They're not coming.</i></b></font>

858
00:39:12,684 --> 00:39:14,357
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>$3,600?</i></b></font>

859
00:39:14,435 --> 00:39:16,529
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Should be enough to cover your
rent for the last three months.</i></b></font>

860
00:39:16,604 --> 00:39:18,857
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't understand.
The clinic has a fund</i></b></font>

861
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:20,032
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to help
with this kind of thing.</i></b></font>

862
00:39:20,108 --> 00:39:21,360
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And we do it
all the time.</i></b></font>

863
00:39:21,776 --> 00:39:22,993
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But...</i></b></font>

864
00:39:23,069 --> 00:39:24,241
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This is from you.</i></b></font>

865
00:39:24,529 --> 00:39:26,497
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's just quicker to do it
from my account.</i></b></font>

866
00:39:26,573 --> 00:39:27,870
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Red tape and all that.</i></b></font>

867
00:39:30,368 --> 00:39:31,870
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't know what to say.</i></b></font>

868
00:39:31,953 --> 00:39:34,513
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Say you'll take that to your
landlord first thing in the morning.</i></b></font>

869
00:39:34,539 --> 00:39:36,883
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And if they do anything but
give you a written receipt,</i></b></font>

870
00:39:36,958 --> 00:39:39,086
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you call me right away.</i></b></font>

871
00:39:39,669 --> 00:39:41,467
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I will. Thank you.</i></b></font>

872
00:39:48,845 --> 00:39:50,643
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're back.
I am.</i></b></font>

873
00:39:50,805 --> 00:39:53,103
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I heard you took care
of my client.</i></b></font>

874
00:39:54,976 --> 00:39:56,102
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thanks, Louis.</i></b></font>

875
00:39:56,477 --> 00:39:57,774
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're welcome.</i></b></font>

876
00:39:58,813 --> 00:40:01,191
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But we're partners,
and they're all our clients.</i></b></font>

877
00:40:01,649 --> 00:40:02,775
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They are.</i></b></font>

878
00:40:03,735 --> 00:40:04,736
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Louis,</i></b></font>

879
00:40:05,153 --> 00:40:08,373
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I didn't mean it when I said you
weren't ready to be managing partner.</i></b></font>

880
00:40:09,490 --> 00:40:10,662
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes, you did.</i></b></font>

881
00:40:10,992 --> 00:40:11,993
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe I did.</i></b></font>

882
00:40:12,243 --> 00:40:13,665
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But the truth is,</i></b></font>

883
00:40:13,745 --> 00:40:15,167
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not ready either.</i></b></font>

884
00:40:16,915 --> 00:40:20,715
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do you say we both act
as interim managing partners?</i></b></font>

885
00:40:22,211 --> 00:40:23,554
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'd be honored.</i></b></font>

886
00:40:26,758 --> 00:40:28,135
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It seems to me
the first order of business</i></b></font>

887
00:40:28,217 --> 00:40:30,561
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>is what are we gonna do
about the name of the firm?</i></b></font>

888
00:40:32,472 --> 00:40:34,065
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't know
about you, but...</i></b></font>

889
00:40:35,725 --> 00:40:37,978
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I think we should keep it
exactly the same.</i></b></font>

890
00:40:38,061 --> 00:40:39,233
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Me, too.</i></b></font>

891
00:40:40,188 --> 00:40:43,158
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I mean, you never know when she's
gonna want to come back, right?</i></b></font>

892
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:46,870
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, Louis, you never know.</i></b></font>

893
00:40:55,703 --> 00:40:57,250
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What are you two
still doing here?</i></b></font>

894
00:40:57,872 --> 00:40:59,124
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We've still got
12 hours.</i></b></font>

895
00:40:59,207 --> 00:41:01,881
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We're not going to stop trying
to keep Sofia in her apartment.</i></b></font>

896
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:03,212
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Good for you.</i></b></font>

897
00:41:04,545 --> 00:41:06,547
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But you don't have
to do it tonight.</i></b></font>

898
00:41:09,050 --> 00:41:11,098
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Turns out she got
a little grace period.</i></b></font>

899
00:41:12,011 --> 00:41:13,388
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How did she get that?</i></b></font>

900
00:41:14,055 --> 00:41:16,604
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's amazing what you can do when
you care about your clients.</i></b></font>

901
00:41:19,769 --> 00:41:21,817
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then I guess
first thing tomorrow,</i></b></font>

902
00:41:22,522 --> 00:41:24,240
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>we should plan
our next move.</i></b></font>

903
00:41:25,233 --> 00:41:26,701
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I guess we should.</i></b></font>

